---
title: One-Pan Chicken Sausage Pizza-Dillas with Bell Pepper & Marinara Sauce
description: [In your best Jerry Seinfeld voice]: “What’s the deal with the pizza-dilla? Is it pizza? Is it quesadilla? Make up your mind!” Well, Jerry, we’re here to tell you, these pizza-dillas are the best of both worlds: Quesadillas loaded with your favorite pizza toppings, like gooey mozzarella and Italian cheese, bell pepper, and Italian chicken sausage in a tangy marinara sauce. But what makes pizza-dilla better than pizza? The flour tortillas are quicker to cook than pizza dough, making this meal a one-pan weeknight wonder. That sounds like a pretty good i-dilla to us!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/one-pan-chicken-sausage-pizza-dillas-444e8cb5.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/one-pan-chicken-sausage-pizza-dillas-6203c53795bd8032f17ccd2b-1e339958.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/one-pan-chicken-sausage-pizza-dillas-6203c53795bd8032f17ccd2b
time required: 20 minutes
author: HelloFresh
cuisine: North America
course: main course
nutrition:
  calories: 770 kcal
